Key Match Events: Golden State Warriors defeated New Orleans Pelicans with a final score of 104-89.
Moses Moody contributed significantly with 15 points and 9 rebounds.
Jonathan Kuminga scored 16 points off the bench.
Jordan Hawkins was the top scorer for the Pelicans with 23 points.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game was held at Chase Center in San Francisco, CA.
The referees for the game were Dedric Taylor, Ben Taylor, and Matt Kallio.
